product_desc:

The idea is to share the road between the car owner and the passenger. In other words, car owner can make an account on garaak, promote it as a car owner and add his data, car photos and driver's license to be verified that it is activated. After accepting him/her as a driver, he/she can add trips, choose the number of available chairs and identify the price of the chair. That's it.

name: Telecosys
product_desc:
Telecom operators and many other service providers operate using two types of platforms; service platforms and charging platforms. Service platforms are the platforms that allows the use of service for customers, it determines which service each customer would have and how they are going to use it. The charging platforms charges the customers for the services they have used on the service platforms.

The customer data at the service provider is spanned over those different platforms for either service enabling or for charging purposes. Any inconsistency in the customer data among those platforms will lead to either Revenue Leakage or Bad Customer Experience.


Telecosys’ product is VeriSure Online Data Integrity Checker; a new innovative software solution that directly integrates with the different IT/network platforms (service and charging platforms) to do a 360-degree customer data check across all platforms to automatically detect, report, and fix Data Integrity

name: Lens
product_desc:
Lens lets you capture photos that are verified and then watermarked by date, time & location. You’ll never ask when or where a photo was taken again!

Nowadays content we view is lost in a sea of distribution because there is no way to verify it, it lacks the 'when' & 'where'. There is a missing link between when a photo or video is taken, & when it is viewed by someone. That missing link is verification - the when & where any photo or video was taken - & Lens provides the solution to this by pulling the date & time from our servers & the location from the phone’s GPS. More importantly though, we watermark all this information ON the actual image, making it easily visible to anyone viewing it.

Verification is important for all kinds of reasons. In the news when viewing a photo or video, if you’re late to work because of an accident on the road, work documentation whether in construction, architecture, & home or travel listings.
high_concept: Capture more than what you see.

name: Codly

It consists of three main parts:

- An Adobe Photoshop extension to help designers to slice the PSD into images and control the app workflow. 

- Live-Preview, which is a mobile application that allows the designer to preview the application under development on unlimited number of mobile devices.  

- Finally, the cloud based service which is responsible for exporting application assets for different devices and resolutions, generating source code for different platforms.

Also we are building a unique marketplace where designers sell their Codly compatible designs, and developers or anyone can buy designs like (login screen, home, ...) with source code.

name: Chaino
product_desc:
Chaino: www.chaino.com

Chaino has grown 400% over the last 2 months because it solves a simple problem.
Community owners who use created and nurtured a community on Facebook have a major problem. Facebook simply doesn't allow them to organically reach a significant percentage of the community they worked hard to build. Not only this, Facebook drives to pay to reach these users instead of sharing the returns with them. Moreover, Facebook Pages’ feature set is not geared towards engaging and activating communities.

We validated that this pain point is real by reaching out to 2 community admins over March and April. The result was 15,000 users registered via these admins in 2 months. Our focus now is on completing the features requested by our budding community influencers ASAP to further engage these users.
The quickest way to get an overview of what Chaino provides to normal members is to watch this 2-minute video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_GEwoIkMWys

In Middle East & Africa, less than 4% of the population has a credit card and even fewer of these small segments own US credit cards yet goods imported from the US continue to be quite popular and in order to bridge the gap between Middle East & Africa and the West, Edfa3ly.com handles all issues of the sale, ranging from the payment transaction to government taxes and even shipping and delivery to the customers door step.

Middle Eastern & African consumers can browse any American e-commerce site, select an item for purchase and calculate the total cost of their order (including shipping and customs taxes) before placing the order.
high_concept: Bridge for Middle Eastern & African Consumers to shop the world

name: Simplex
product_desc:
Simplex is offering simple industrial solutions. Simplex’s first product is a customizable CNC (computer numerical control – an automated cutting and engraving machine). This means a computer converts the design produced by Computer Aided Design software (CAD), into numbers. The numbers can be considered to be the coordinates of a graph and they control the movement of the cutter. In this way the computer controls the cutting and shaping of the material that is being shaped and developed.
he process starts with CAD design or any photo on a computer. After downloading it to the machine it will drill and cut the desired design in a 2D or 3D shape, on any type of material using router (for wood), plasma, laser (for steel) or water jet (for marble).

Zaagel tackles this issue and provides a faster and cheaper way for delivering items using the power of the crowd. Zaagel is a delivery service based on crowdsourcing. We enable any individual to become a courier and deliver items in return of a monetary reward. People simply list the products they want to buy on Zaagel.com and anyone in the crowd can earn money by going to our website and choosing the products they can deliver. We currently focus on international deliveries and we plan to make this platform available for local brands and retail stores.

name: QHat
product_desc: QHat is a cloud-based Loyalty Platform allowing businesses to improve their customers’ loyalty, retention, advocacy and lifetime value. The QHat Loyalty Platform consists of the Loyalty Program Engine (LPE), the Customer Engagement Manager (CEM) and the Customer Intelligence Appliance (CIA). The LPE allows merchants through a self service interface to configure every aspect of the program. Thanks to QHat Smart Codes (QSC) generated using a proprietary encoding algorithm, QHat programs require no hardware, no connection to QHat backend and zero upfront cost. A QSC is represented as a QR code and as an alphanumeric string. The CEM provides merchants with an effective 2-way engagement tool with advanced targeting capabilities to deliver personalized messages to customers across multiple communication channels. QHat CIA provides merchants with valuable customer insights where they get to rediscover their customers and learn more about their demographics, purchasing trends and much more.
markets: Loyalty Programs, Social Media Marketing, Email Marketing
